title: 128: Our Lost Possessions (Rabbit Hole) | Ear Biscuits Ep. 128
description:
On your death bed, you receive a box with all the items you've ever lost is returned to you. R&L discuss how they'd feel in this situation as they dive down another rabbit hole on this week's Ear Biscuits.
